text: Allianz SE is a German financial services company. It is headquartered in Munich, Germany. The company is a component of the Euro Stoxx 50 stock market index. The company was founded in 1890. It has over 70 countries and has around 147,000 employees. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:1890 establishments in Europe Category:1890s establishments in Germany
